<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink83-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">varainta aṇumaikkaṇṇē talaimakaṟkup puṟattoḻukkam uṇṭākiyavaḻi ataṉai aṟinta talaivi avaṉōṭu pulantu colliyatu.
      </p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink83">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>maṇantaṉai yaruḷā yāyiṉum paipayat</l>
<l>taṇantaṉai yāki yuymmō nummū</l>
<l>roṇṭoṭi muṉkai yāyamun</l>
<l>taṇṭuṟai yūraṉ peṇṭeṉap paṭaṟkē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

<l>   You united [with me] </l> 
<l>   and yet you show [me] no consideration. </l> 
<l>   Leave quietly and go to your village!  </l> 
<l>   So that [I] might be called </l> 
<l>   'the woman of the man from the village by the cool ghat' </l> 
<l>   by the girls of your village </l> 
<l>   with bright bangles on their forearms. </l> 
<p/>
<l>   OR: So that the girls of your village </l> 
<l>   with bright bangles on their forearms</l> 
<l>   might be called </l> 
<l>   'the women of the man from the village by the cool ghat'.  </l> 

    
    
          </lg>
    </div>
